summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Sunnyside Avenue from north line of Baltimore Addition to No. 42 Street et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing sewers under Ordinance No. 16873 creating Local Improvement District No. 1582 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
